Screenshot2Docx:
 - Simple java tool to take screenshot and append it to word document.
 - On clicking screenshot button, the tool disappears,, takes screenshot and reappears again
Feautures :
 - Takes Full ScreenShot and append it to the word document.
 - Ability to add text to the word document via text box.
 - Ability to capture part of the screen. Screen Area is the area of the tool itself. Resize the tool window to take only that part of the background screen
 - Tool is included with Image Editor for highlighting and adding text to the image itself.
How To Run :
 - The maven build produces an executable jar.